409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"廢佬話係火魔燒雜物釋出喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fb08f93e68df50fdff822f1d0a3bff5b3b3b73","tid":1739209,"uid":141664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91338f9b040cc1fa5f4d39288a7bbf33189c055a","tid":1739209,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"廢佬話係火魔燒雜物釋出喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"Dioxin 係要有Chlorinated materials如 Vinyl, PVC 燒先有Dioxin 出， 水馬係PE 無 Chlorine , 但一般車軑同雪糕筒下面如果有黑色嚿重膠座係有PVC的"},{"pid":"83e24ab747499b27b390527c260ab2f10459a3ea","tid":1739209,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22fb08f93e68df50fdff822f1d0a3bff5b3b3b73","tid":1739209,"uid":141664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91338f9b040cc1fa5f4d39288a7bbf33189c055a","tid":1739209,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"廢佬話係火魔燒雜物釋出喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"Dioxin 係要有Chlorinated materials如 Vinyl, PVC 燒先有Dioxin 出， 水馬係PE 無 Chlorine , 但一般車軑同雪糕筒下面如果有黑色嚿重膠座係有PVC的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"kkwong段文咪有講<br />\npvc難燒著<br />\n要高溫先出二噁英"},{"pid":"80b6837dd57c6f5a4c7e8b21f07789efc7c5bb1e","tid":1739209,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:59:35.000Z","msg":"汪 Sir 話係燒膠同雜物產生二噁英，入示威者數咁喎⋯⋯咪住！<br />\n<br />\n要燒到出二噁英，要有氯 Cl 同 有機物及温度高。<br />\n<br />\n燒乜膠先燒到有二噁英呢？主要有PVC（3號膠：少部份深色嘅膠桶、電線），佢有氯，係有機物。由於 PVC 本身有毒，呢幾十年已經被 PP（5號膠）及 PE(HDPE)（2號膠）取代。示威者唔易係街揾到 PVC。<br />\n<br />\n由於 PVC 含碳量 (38.4%) 比 PP 及 PE (85.7%) 為低，PVC 較難點著燒得，而燒著會又臭又乸鼻，示威者好少玩 PVC，就算燒著都温度低。不如汪汪 Sir 做吓實驗，睇吓 PVC 造嘅膠箱／桶係咪咁易著火啦！<br />\n<br />\n垃圾焚化爐燒 PVC 出到二噁英係因為温度夠高，你係街度開放式咁燒 PVC 係冇咁高温。出到 dioxins 嘅機會唔係冇，但好低！<br />\n<br />\nPP 及 PE 易著火，好好燒，又周圍都有，所以主要係燒佢，冇氯，所以冇二噁英。<br />\n其它垃圾係冇乜氯，所以燒到出二噁英嘅機會好低。<br />\n<br />\n結論：所以咪轉移視線啦，二噁英係中國催淚彈造成嘅！<br />\n<br />\n立場copy返黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%92%AA%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%B7%9A%E5%95%A6-%E4%BA%8C%E5%99%81%E8%8B%B1%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%98%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2592%25AA%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%2595%25A6-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%2599%2581%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BF%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2598%2585%2F&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqK0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=95968526\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2592%25AA%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%2595%25A6-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%2599%2581%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BF%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2598%2585%2F&h=79b4c7b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%92%AA%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%B7%9A%E5%95%A6-%E4%BA%8C%E5%99%81%E8%8B%B1%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%98%85/</a><br />\nsource 係k kwong fb"},{"pid":"b4be4c85130db10525d141e1b12dff78b50df05e","tid":1739209,"uid":141664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83e24ab747499b27b390527c260ab2f10459a3ea","tid":1739209,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22fb08f93e68df50fdff822f1d0a3bff5b3b3b73","tid":1739209,"uid":141664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91338f9b040cc1fa5f4d39288a7bbf33189c055a","tid":1739209,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:10:43.000Z","msg":"廢佬話係火魔燒雜物釋出喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"Dioxin 係要有Chlorinated materials如 Vinyl, PVC 燒先有Dioxin 出， 水馬係PE 無 Chlorine , 但一般車軑同雪糕筒下面如果有黑色嚿重膠座係有PVC的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"kkwong段文咪有講<br />\npvc難燒著<br />\n要高溫先出二噁英"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:03:38.000Z","msg":"PVC 本來係做Industrial Tough Application, 但如果大火一樣燒著同出毒煙，新一代建築都唔會再用PVC, Dioxin 400-700 Deg C 就燒得出 850 Deg C 以上就分解"},{"pid":"f45ce8c1a76a99a2b5860be6e568a2de3814face","tid":1739209,"uid":264891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgfSH1k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgfSH1k.png&h=531b7e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7RRYzG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7RRYzG.png&h=ff858d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dBB9Go.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dBB9Go.png&h=5dd01e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ReW9GO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ReW9GO.png&h=cc533191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Opegqe9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOpegqe9.png&h=d91979fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5uTstw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5uTstw.png&h=a5639f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人讀化學出生所以知道dioxin到底有幾可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塞維索事件為發生於1976年7月10日12時37分的工業事故，位於意大利倫巴第大區米蘭北方約20公里的小型化學工廠，為史上最嚴重的2,3,7,8-四氯雙苯-p-戴奧辛（TCDD）污染事件<br />\n<br />\n1976年時，塞維索一家化學工廠的三氯酚反應器因為冷卻水不足，使外側的蒸汽渦輪將反應器的升溫至攝氏300度，導致反應失控，大量戴奧辛及其他有毒物洩出。附近土地受到嚴重污染，隨後有大量動物死亡，居民也陸續發生各種病變，即為塞維索事件。<br />\n<br />\n該事件促進了相關科學研究及工業安全規範的制定，歐洲聯盟的工業安全法規又被稱作塞維索II指令（英語：Directive 96/82/EC）。"},{"pid":"2d0a8449cd6ff3deffa865aee2a800a2d2b7a449","tid":1739209,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d150e1fa26c0ef9232e32daae3461e90f7a138e2","tid":1739209,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80919b69ce44f7247f62a4b2836bc8340931a27a","tid":1739209,"uid":244693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa5f2e60b5fd4f2ad188096d3c4cbb5d45486909","tid":1739209,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22b2409534e67cbf91b6f1d0dcdfc35adf87298","tid":1739209,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee89ce915b7404e158e176d0368aa90c44bf259c","tid":1739209,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}